TITLE: Exposing Component with Code Splitting - React 18
DESCRIPTION: This snippet showcases how 'app2' exposes the 'Content' component for use by other applications. It also implements code splitting by leveraging React.lazy, allowing the component to be loaded on-demand, thereby optimizing resource usage.
SOURCE: https://github.com/module-federation/module-federation-examples/blob/master/react-18-code-splitting/README.md#2025-04-21_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
import React from 'react';

const Content = () => {
    return <div>This is the Content component!</div>;
};

export default Content;

```

