TITLE: Configuring Module Federation Plugin in Remote
DESCRIPTION: This code snippet configures the ModuleFederationPlugin in the remote application's webpack configuration. It defines the name of the module, the filename for the remote entry point, and the modules to expose, specifically the './pkg/' directory, which contains the compiled Wasm module.
SOURCE: https://github.com/module-federation/module-federation-examples/blob/master/rust-wasm/README.md#2025-04-21_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: JavaScript
CODE:
```
new ModuleFederationPlugin({
  name: "GameOfLifeModule",
  filename: "remoteEntry.js",
  exposes: {
    "./GameOfLifeModule": "./pkg/",
  },
}),
```

