TITLE: Implementing Custom Skip Test Command in Cypress
DESCRIPTION: Creates a custom Cypress command to conditionally skip tests based on specific conditions
SOURCE: https://github.com/module-federation/module-federation-examples/blob/master/cypress-e2e/README.md#2025-04-21_snippet_16

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
declare global {
  namespace Cypress {
    interface Chainable {
      skipWhen(condition: boolean): void;
    }
  }
}

Cypress.Commands.add('skipWhen', function (condition) {
  if (condition) {
    this.skip();
  }
});
```

